---
title: Pork Sausage Gnocchi Bake with Roasted Tomatoes & a Crispy Panko Topping
description: Raise your hand if you’re obsessed with anything involving gnocchi. While we can’t actually see you, we’re right there with you! If you’re new to gnocchi, it’s a pasta/dumpling hybrid that’s partially-made with potatoes, resulting in an extra-tender, extra-carby bite. Here, it’s paired with pork sausage and juicy roasted tomato wedges, then tossed in a savory lemon sauce. To top things off—in this case literally—there’s a layer of cheesy panko. Once baked, it turns golden and crunchy, making it the perfect contrast to the creamy melange below.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-sausage-gnocchi-bake-474bb909.jpg
